articles.author: Abbie Cheeseman, John Hudson, Missy Ryan, Michael Birnbaum
articles.title: Syrian rebels deliver American to U.S. military post, photos show - The Washington Post
articles.description: Travis Timmerman, a Missouri native, was imprisoned in Syria after he crossed into the country months ago. He was flown out of Syria and taken by helicopter to Jordan on Friday, a U.S. official said.
articles.content: An American citizen jailed in Syria was handed to the U.S. government and taken to Jordan on Friday, U.S. and Syrian officials said, after he was freed during the chaotic collapse of the Assad regime… [+287 chars]
